        "content": "<p>How can I setup format on save with VS Code?</p>",
        "id": 419173393,
        "sender_full_name": "Shawn",
        "timestamp": 1706762196
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>If you use the unofficial vscode extension (<a href=\"https://github.com/ivan-demchenko/roc-vscode-unofficial\">https://github.com/ivan-demchenko/roc-vscode-unofficial</a>) with LSP configured then something like this works for me:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"JSON\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"nt\">\"roc-lang.language-server.exe\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"/path/to/roc_ls\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"nt\">\"editor.formatOnSave\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kc\">true</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"nt\">\"editor.formatOnSaveMode\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"file\"</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 419245517,
        "sender_full_name": "Artur Domurad",
        "timestamp": 1706794005
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/22008/M_sWnyJkNnfQzWcbR5x15r04/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/22008/M_sWnyJkNnfQzWcbR5x15r04/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/22008/M_sWnyJkNnfQzWcbR5x15r04/image.png\"></a></div>",
